Introduction

Jeon Woong, popularly known as Woong, is a South Korean singer and music producer from Brand New Music. He started off as a trainee under JYP, Woolim, and YG Entertainment before eventually joining his current label. After years of extensive training, Woong made his official debut in 2019 as the main vocalist of the boy group AB6IX.
